    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"His I.Q. is over 200.. He's a freakin Genius!\"</em></p><h5 id=\"prerequisites\">Prerequisites</h5><p>Have the Exploit Weakness feature</p><h5 id=\"benefit\">Benefit</h5><p>You possess an unnaturally high battle I.Q. When targeting a creature who is under the effects of your Exploit Weakness feature, you may prematurely end its effects to grant yourself either +3 to a single attack against the creature who was under the effects of your Exploit Weakness Feature or to lower the next saving throw of the creature was under the effects of your Exploit Weakness feature by 2.</p>",
